N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 163.15 - Discriminatory practices

State Regulations

Approved entities may not refuse enrollment by reason of a
person or persons particular race, color, religion, national origin, age, sex, sexual orientation, disability, gender identity, military status, familial
status or any other protected category under any Federal, State or local
law. Notes
